summary: I am losing my mind at how ‘Mother’s Basement’ on youtube describes the season finale of SAO Alicization. I have never watched...
body:
I am losing my mind at how ‘Mother’s Basement’ on youtube describes the season finale of SAO Alicization. I have never watched any SAO and I am DYING;

“So, for NO reason, Cardinal anti climactically eats shit and dies.

But then Ujio has a brain wave!

“Wait a second…

If those swords are made of people… Maybe I can be made of SWORDS!”

(yeah that’s really where this is going)

Using the last of Cardinal’s power, he T-poses to assert dominance, fuses with his sword, and transforms into the Dragoon from Kirby Air-ride.”

Video source

summary:
My Genius Soulmate (Phan AU) [On Hold] - Chapter 24//Dan (on Wattpad) https://my.w.tt/iXTgPrz2wX

If numbers on your wrist...
caption:
My Genius Soulmate (Phan AU) [On Hold] - Chapter 24//Dan (on Wattpad) https://my.w.tt/iXTgPrz2wX If numbers on your wrist controlled one of the most important aspects of your life, how would you feel? For Dan Howell this is a thing that causes much stress and discomfort in his life. Dan likes to know how things work and this is something that he has tried and failed many times to understand. Phil Lester hasn’t given much thought to the clock on his wrist. He doesn’t see the point in worrying over something that he can’t change. When these two worlds collide what questions will be answered? What will be built and what might they lose? *SPIN OFF OF MY KILLER SOUMATE*
